<div type="abstract"><head>Offener Brief des Rates</head><p>Der Rat gibt Ulrich I. Grundherr und Seitz Geuder, Bürger zu Nürnberg, Vollmacht zur Vertretung vor dem Landgericht zu Sulzbach wegen der Lehen des verstorbenen Friedrich Schenk von Reicheneck.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_365" id="182r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"/>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_365_r1l2">Wir ~ dıe <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> des Rats der Stat cʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> <expan>Bek<ex>ennen</ex></expan> <expan>offenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_365_r1l3">mit diſem brief / daʒ vvir <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Grunth<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> vnd Seıcʒen Gewder </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_365_r1l4"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> burgern <expan>gegeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gancʒen vnd <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_365_r1l7">gevvalt 
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒ </del> ein <expan>erfaru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> cʒetun vnd cʒefragen 
<add><ab facs="#facs_365_line_1571824897344_252">von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen </ab></add> vor dem lantgericht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_365_r1l8">cʒu Sulcʒbach von ſölcher <expan>leh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wegen Als die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> von Schenk </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_365_r1l9"> <expan>Fridrich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von Reichneck 
<del rend="strikethrough">ge </del> ſeligen gehabt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> vvie ſ </del> vvie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_365_r1l10">man ſich fürbaʒ damit halten ſülle / daʒ eʒ den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> vnſch </del> an den - </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_365_r1l11"><expan>ſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Jren <expan>leh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnſchedlich ſeẏ / Mit <expan>vrk<ex>unde</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_365" id="182r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab/></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Wir, die <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> des rats der stat czu
                                <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, <expan>bek<ex>ennen</ex></expan>
<expan>offenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> mit disem brief, daz wir
                                <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Grunth<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> und Seiczen Gewder,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> burgern, <expan>gegeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ganczen und
                                <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt, ein
                            <expan>erfaru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> cze tun und cze fragen <add>von
                                    <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen</add> vor dem lantgericht
                        czu Sulczbach von sölcher <expan>leh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wegen, als die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> von Schenk
                            <expan>Fridrich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von Reichneck seligen gehabt
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, wie man sich fürbaz damit halten
                        sülle, daz ez den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> an
                            den<expan>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> iren <expan>leh<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        unschedlich sey. Mit <expan>urk<ex>unde</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
